**`mapSubscriptionStatus` (через handleWebhookPayload):**
- `'active'` → `ACTIVE`
- `'trialing'` → `TRIALING`
- `'past_due'` → `PAST_DUE`
- `'canceled'` → `CANCELED`
- `'incomplete'` → `INCOMPLETE`
- `'unpaid'` → `UNPAID`
- `'incomplete_expired'` → `CANCELED`
- `'paused'` → `UNKNOWN`
- Невідомий статус → `UNKNOWN`

